        "timestamp": "2020-02-14 08:11:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified-1 Code-Review-1\n\nTested it in lab and on infra server the contents of resolv.conf weren't preserved after reboot:\n\nBefore reboot:\n\n[root@infra ~]# cat resolv.conf \nnameserver 8.8.8.8\nnameserver 10.8.8.10\n# Generated by NetworkManager\nsearch openstacklocal novalocal\nnameserver 10.8.8.2\n\n\nAfter:\n[root@infra ~]# cat /etc/resolv.conf \n# Generated by NetworkManager\nsearch novalocal\n\n\n\n\n[root@infra ~]# grep -v ^# /etc/NetworkManager/NetworkManager.conf \n[main]\ndns=none\n[logging]",
        "patchset_number": 2
